dc_title_s: The Daily Telegraph war map no. 12
dc_description_s: 1 meter = 3.28 feet about 3 feet 3 inches.; "On a very large scale of about 3/4 inch to 1 mile, contains more information than any existing map of the same area."; Includes inset and glossary.; Index map inside cover.; Map of Gallipoli Peninsula showing forts, roads and tracks.; Relief shown by gradient tints, and spot heights.|82 x 54 centimeters|Scale approximately 1:90,000|General Map Collection
